SPECIFICATION
	
	A cron monitor to remove all cron entries older than 30 days from all users
		
This script is written in python.

It is
	fully unit tested
	fully configurable
	fully validated
	fully commented
	easy to maintain

How To Install

 	1. append the following line to your crontab ( as root)

		0 * * * * python /path/to/cron_monitor.py
		e.g) 0 * * * * python /root/work/cron\ monitor/monitor/cron_monitor.py

 	2. now it works


How To Run Unit test for cron monitor

	#cd /path/to/cron\ monitor/
	#python test.py
	
